title: Nantucket 4pc Bedroom Set - Twin Bed - w/Trundle and Storage Drawer
description: The Nantucket youth bedroom is not your average "kiddie" bedroom. Traditional in styling with a hint of cottage detail, it features beadboard accents and a rich espresso finish. The Nantucket combines style, sturdiness, and storage to create the perfect bedroom group to see your child from toddler through teen.

title: Nantucket Bed Set - Twin - w/Trundle and Storage Drawer
description: The Nantucket youth bedroom is not your average "kiddie" bedroom. Traditional in styling with a hint of cottage detail, it features beadboard accents and a rich espresso finish. Constructed of solid wood with wood composites and a combination of Ash and Asian hardwood veneers. The Nantucket is strong, sturdy furniture meant to stand up to the test of time and use. Larger than most youth bedroom sets, the Nantucket case goods are a great fit to transition your little one from childhood into young adulthood. The bed, available in Twin or Full sized, has a slat support system eliminating the need for a box spring. Also available with both bed sizes is the matching under-bed storage drawer/trundle. Whether you need extra storage space or an additional bed, this option meets your needs. Speaking of storage, the Nantucket bedroom provides plenty of storage options in the coordinating nightstand, dresser, chest, and TV chest. The dresser provides 3 drawers and a sliding door with an adjustable shelf behind, plus a matching mirror. The chest offers 5 drawers of storage. The nightstand has one drawer and an open lower shelf. The TV chest has a sliding door with adjustable shelf behind and an open area with a drawer and adjustable shelf, providing ample space for electronics, game units and such. All drawers have recessed pulls in an aged pewter finish, dovetail drawer construction and full-extension ball-bearing drawer glides for years of trouble free use. The Nantucket combines style, sturdiness, and storage to create the perfect bedroom group to see your child from toddler through teen.

description: Straightforward and unassuming, the Springfield Bed is the simple design solution for bedrooms in need of an easy design twist, or an easy palette for colorful aesthetics. The simple rectangular headboard and footboard are covered in sleek, faux leather, and are available in either brown or white. Available in twin only, it has the added convenience of arriving in a single box. Matching rails are included. The platform design does not require a box spring. Some assembly required.
